I worked hard to convince

71
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,639
Lidong to take on this role.

72
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:50,039
You know your situation.

73
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,519
If you can't cooperate,

74
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,919
there's nothing I can do.

75
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,479
It's not my millions on the line.

76
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,079
Fine, fine.

77
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:59,250
I'll agree to that.

78
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,330
Go on.

79
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,730
And these.

80
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:18,020
(Chauffeur service, five-star hotel,
three meals plus supper.)

81
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:40,130
Why do you have
so many men's clothes at home?

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,130
Collection.

83
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,810
This one looks good. Go change.

84
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:38,810
What's wrong?

85
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,010
Tie my tie.

86
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,130
Here, let me put it on for you.

87
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,730
I'll grab a watch.

88
